            , <rs id="t17770702-77-cd348" type="crimeDate">June 24th</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17770702-77-off347 t17770702-77-cd348"></join>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17770702-77-person617">
                  JOSEPH
                   SAMUEL
               <interp inst="t17770702-77-person617" type="surname" value="SAMUEL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770702-77-person617" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770702-77-person617" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>On the 24th of June I was driving a cart; I bought an old livery surtout coat, and put it on the copse of the cart; I went from the cart about two minutes, upon my return the coat was gone.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17770702-77-person618">
                  JOHN
                   CARPENTER
               <interp inst="t17770702-77-person618" type="surname" value="CARPENTER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770702-77-person618" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770702-77-person618" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am apprentice to a pawnbroker; the cart stopped opposite our shop; I saw the prisoner take the coat off the copse and run away; I followed and overtook him, and he said he belonged to the cart; he was taken about an hour after; I am certain to his person.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17770702-77-person619">
                  PHILIP
                   CROCKFIELD
               <interp inst="t17770702-77-person619" type="surname" value="CROCKFIELD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770702-77-person619" type="given" value="PHILIP"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770702-77-person619" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>The coat was pawned with me by another person.</p>
               <p>[The coat was produced in Court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.]</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I had the coat, but did not take it off the cart.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17770702-77-verdict349" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17770702-77-verdict349" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the Second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
